comments: Green (HOU) and Caldwell-Pope (DEN) come together off-ball and marginal contact occurs. Caldwell-Pope's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball goes out of bounds after Jokic (DEN) loses possession of the ball while dribbling.
Sengun (HOU) initiates contact to Jokic's (DEN) head as he gains possession of the rebound.
Braun (DEN) initiates contact to Green's (HOU) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
As Jokic (DEN) begins to dribble, Green (HOU) reaches in and marginal contact occurs to  Jokic's arm.
Jackson (DEN) wraps Sengun (HOU), which affects his FOM during the pick.
Sengun (HOU) establishes himself in Jackson's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jackson (DEN) makes contact with VanVleet's (HOU) arm after the release, which affects his follow-through on the jump shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) commits a take foul on Tate (HOU).
Caldwell-Pope commits a take foul on VanVleet (HOU).
Tate (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball during the inbound play, any additional contact with Porter Jr (DEN) is considered incidental.
Jokic (DEN) commits a take foul on Green (HOU).
Porter Jr (DEN) commits a take foul on Brooks (HOU).
Brooks (HOU) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
